unications/campaigns/beta_campaign/icons/icon_04.png</ThumbnailImage><xPower Type="GroupStart" GroupStart="" Name="IntroText" label="Intro Text" readonly="false" hidden="false" required="false" Expanded="true"><IntroCopy type="dhtml" label="Intro Text" readonly="false" hidden="false" required="false"><![CDATA[<p>The new BYU-Idaho Web site has a fresh look and feel. This updated style reflects the continual strengthening and enhancement of the university. Variety and flexibility are core features, with a few key elements of style that will soon spread to other university pages and services. The goal is speed, simplicity, and clarity. An official BYU-Idaho page should be recognizable with just a glance.</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p>The site's design will constantly-yet subtly-evolve to match current Internet conventions and the university's own changing needs. Watch for mobile versions next!</p>
