<div class="ccl">
<p><strong>New Look and Feel</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>The new site features large, vivid images that help tell the story of BYU-Idaho.</li>
<li>Official university colors and fonts have been incorporated into the new design.</li>
<li>Research and testing has given the university insight into how the new web design can help the user experience.</li>
</ul>
</div>
